Class Picture

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.ImageIcon
      • Picture
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.Icon
    public class Picture
extends javax.swing.ImageIcon
    This class represents a graphical picture. Once an instance of this is created, it can be used to create Swing components showing that picture, including JButton and JLabel.
